posts.title: President Trump has been hosting calls with Trump Force 47 members.
posts.content:
To become a Trump Force 47 member, all you have to do is sign up at Trumpforce47.com which will provide you with a list of 10 Trump supporters near you who do not always vote. All you do is let them know what voting options are available to them.

As hard as it is to fathom, there are Trump supporters who do not vote. I just recently talked to a guy who owns his own business and never has time to vote.

President Trump has been hosting phone calls with Trump Force 47 members. This is an opportunity of a lifetime to Save America.
